{
  "stem": "628.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They took us through the fields, because the SS had to go on the streets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were running away from the Russians, or going to the Russians-- I don't know what happened there-- for military use.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we had a wagon with a horse, which the SS put their-- their belongings on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know that the horse, in the middle of the what's it called, on the fields, so high snow, suddenly that horse couldn't push anymore.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So they took the horse on the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the prisoners-- we had to do the-- the what's it called, do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "People were-- anybody who was sitting down to take a-- a commission, to shit or piss or something, they couldn't get up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because once you took your hands-- you didn't have gloves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You didn't have really shoe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Once you sit down, they couldn't get up, from the cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So the SS, you didn't hear nothing else but poof-- shooting-- poof.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When you looked back, all dead bodies on that road, lying, on the-- on the-- on that march-- all dead, all dead.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we said hun-- we said, food, food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came into a little-- little village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put us into a what's it called.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's written in the books, even-- into a little farmhouse-- ice cold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have any-- you know, marching.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they must have given us pork soup, you know, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody got diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We shit, and we shit, because we-- we didn't eat for days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next day, in the [GERMAN, you know, where the [GERMAN] they came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, not one, they went with their [? carbines, ?] with their knives, into the thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If this was somebody left, that one little Jew, they didn't want to leave behind.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
